The '''''Intruder''''' was a [[Victory II-class Star Destroyer/Legends|''Victory II''-class Star Destroyer]] that saw service with the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Navy]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. It was assigned to investigate the [[Azzameen family]]'s raid on the [[Viraxo Industries|Viraxo Shipping]] cargo facility [[Viraxo 54]], located at [[Denbo]].

